        <!-- People -->
        <article id="people" class="panel">
          <header>
            <h2>People</h2>
          </header>
          <p>
            Some generated names and addresses, if you need such
            things. I suppose there's a pretty decent chance they're
            real people and functional addresses too, so don't put
            them into live systems (for which you can use the reserved
            domain
            <a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2606#section-3">&lt;name&gt;@example.com</a>).
          </p>
          <div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="2u"></div>
              <div id="people-container" class="8u">
